				<wikidot:authorName>wishun</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1204404</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Since they have documentation indicating that manifestation progresses beyond 2 seeds, shouldn't that be mentioned in the description? Even if it's just a line something like &quot;&#8230; -2 instances combining larger numbers of -1 exhibit increased size and agression.&quot; or some-such.</p> <p>Minor quibble, good article. Creepiest flower ever. +1</p> <p>Necro-Edit 6 years later: That last entry in the recovered journal shows that our budding entrepreneur may be an idiot, but he's no fool! When you live in the scp-verse, when your buddy goes missing you <em>don't</em> go looking. You set the building on fire and GTFO.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
